OL,7,FHealthcare professionals have urged the
OL,8,FGovernment to step in to address a
OL,9,Fwidespread shortage of antibiotics to
OL,10,Fensure lives are not put at risk.
OL,12,FIt comes as nine children have died
OL,13,Ffrom invasive Group A Strep infections
OL,14,Fin the UK since September.
OL,16,FHealthcare professionals around the
OL,17,Fcountry have reported shortages of
OL,18,Fpenicillin, particularly amoxicillin,
OL,19,Fwhich is one of the treatments for the
OL,20,Fbacterial illness.
OL,3,C'I've never seen an antibiotics
OL,4,Cshortage like this,' says pharmacist
OL,5,Cdespite Government denials
